headlines.description: Leeds and Brentford played out a 0-0 draw in the Premier League at Elland Road on Sunday as the hosts failed to move far from the relegation zone.
headlines.shortLinkText: Leeds held to goalless stalemate by Brentford

headlines.description: Erling Haaland netted a hat trick as Manchester City walked away with a comfortable win over Wolverhampton on Sunday at the Etihad.
headlines.shortLinkText: Haaland nets hat trick as Man City thrash Wolves

headlines.description: Late heroics from Eddie Nketiah gave Arsenal a comeback 3-2 win over Manchester United at the Emirates on Sunday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Arsenal claim last-gasp 3-2 win over Man Utd
